casebody.data:
Michael DOBLIN, Plaintiff,
v.
Linda DOBLIN, Defendant-Movant. M-429 September Term 2018
080007 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 11, 2019

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motions for leave to file a motion for counsel fees and costs as within time (M-430) and to file an overlength brief in support of the motion for counsel fees and costs (M-431) are granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the motion for counsel fees and costs (M-432) is granted, payable by Kenneth J. Rosellini, in the amount of $5,000.
